Class MovieBookingController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.SuperController
      • controller.MovieBookingController
  • public class MovieBookingController
extends SuperController
    This Controller class manages anything related to booking of showtimes made by the moviegoer.

                          int age,
                          java.lang.String tId)
        Method to check whether a booking can be inserted, makes sure that seats are available, and age requirement is met
        Parameters:
        name - name of moviegoer
        email - email of moviegoer
        movieDatetime - showtime of the movie as a Date object
        cineplexName - name of cineplex
        cinemaId - cinema ID
        movieName - name of the movie
        seat_book_row - row of the booking
        seat_book_column - column of booking
        final_price - price based on checkPrice()
        age - age of the person
        tId - transaction ID
        Returns:
        Booking object if successful, if not successful, price for booking object will be set to a specific value and subsequently checked at the view
